title: A Guide to Interpreting the Results of MetaDAG Analysis
text:
1 Introduction
As an illustrative example for interpreting metaDAG results, we consider here the Eukaryotes test presented in Section 2.5. Namely, we consider all Eukaryotes from the KEGG database. Experiment github.
